Package de.bcxp.challenge.documentParsing.csv

package de.bcxp.challenge.documentParsing.csv
Provides CSV-specific document parsing utilities.

This package includes generic and specialized parsers for CSV datasets. These classes are responsible for converting CSV files into structured data models used by the application.
